  "instructions": [
    "In a small bowl, mix together crushed allspice berries, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add the mixture to the chicken breast and marinate for at least 30 minutes.",
    "Preheat the bamboo steamer and add 2 cups of water.",
    "Add the chicken breast to the steamer and steam for 8 minutes.",
    "Meanwhile, prepare the vegetables by slicing the red onion, cucumber, and bell pepper.",
    "Chop the fresh parsley and mint.",
    "Warm the ssam wraps by wrapping them in a damp paper towel and microwaving for 20 seconds.",
    "Assemble the wraps by placing a piece of chicken breast on each wrap, followed by the vegetables and herbs.",
    "Drizzle with ghee or coconut oil and serve immediately.",
